(2, 1, 'Terms & Conditions', '<div class=\"container__cms\">    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agreement between\r\n                User and https://www.yo-coach.com</span>            \r\n			<o:p></o:p>        </span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\">Welcome to Yo!Coach. This website is comprised of various\r\n        web pages operated by FATbit.\r\n        https://www.yo-coach.com is offered to you conditioned on your acceptance\r\n        without modification of the terms, conditions, and notices contained herein\r\n        (the \"Terms\"). Your use of https://www.yo-coach.com constitutes your\r\n        agreement to all such Terms. Please read these terms carefully, and keep a copy\r\n        of them for your reference.\r\n            \r\n			<o:p></o:p></span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;\r\n            \r\n			<o:p></o:p></span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\">https://www.yo-coach.com is learning based website..\r\n            \r\n			<o:p></o:p></span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;\r\n            \r\n			<o:p></o:p></span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\">Yo!Coach is a teaching platform for teachers and students to\r\n            connect for learning a foreign language. Teachers set their own rates and\r\n            schedules and students pay for classes within the site, pick a teacher. Teacher\r\n            gets paid weekly for each class completion. Yo!Coach pays out 85% of cost to\r\n            teachers and keeps 15% to keep the site in operation.\r\n            \r\n			<o:p></o:p></span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\">&nbsp;\r\n            \r\n			<o:p></o:p></span></p>    \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span open=\"\" sans\";\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Electronic\r\